Second Department,

February, 1958

(February 17, 1958) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Leonard Wolochen, Appellant.

Motion for leave to appeal as a poor person, to enlarge time and for other relief denied. Present — Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Beldock, Ughetta and Kleinfeld, JJ.
